# OAuth Token Endpoint

Canonical token endpoint for auth.md discovery.

- URI: `https://rodrigocastilho.com/oauth/token`
- Supported grant types:
  - `urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:jwt-bearer`
  - `urn:workos:agent-auth:grant-type:claim`

This static host publishes the contract surface for discovery and documentation. Passive scanners must not attempt side-effecting token exchanges.
